{"tid":2221033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"15歲少年疑示威現場掟水樽 被控公安條例今開審 警員供稱找不到涉案水樽","createTime":"2020-09-28T05:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T06:57:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5466c93a78b0b737b2dfe79e9b67a5f404b535e5","tid":2221033,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"去年11月2日尖沙嘴舉行「人權民主和你Sing」活動，原獲警方發出不反對通知書，惟活動遭警腰斬，爆發警民衝突。當晚旺角有示威者聚集，其間15歲少年被指掟膠水樽但沒擊中人，及後遭在場便衣警員追截制服，被控《公安條例》下在公眾地方擾亂秩序罪，案件今在西九龍法院少年法庭開審。現場警員供稱，他目擊被告掟水樽，惟事後返回現場嘗試尋找涉案水樽，卻找不到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200928/OQORNPQFRRGLXJSYM3KQ27KPH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200928%2FOQORNPQFRRGLXJSYM3KQ27KPH4%2F&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=20a2a11b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200928%2FOQORNPQFRRGLXJSYM3KQ27KPH4%2F&h=788b84ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200928/OQORNPQFRRGLXJSYM3KQ27KPH4/</a>"},{"pid":"6280d5ff44502de069019897e1318c3e5c75a6dd","tid":2221033,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:47:04.000Z","msg":"阿sir 做野唔洗你教<br />\n<br />\n我話有就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795c5dd7bc52772899819988f1eed48e663e81ce","tid":2221033,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a465732eb904a51a10814dbd7